  var K = ["Aggregate open per-country channel lists into one auto-updating, deduped M3U.","+ Add list","Import","Playlists link to publicly-listed free-to-air streams from the open iptv-org per-country catalogs. WayHop serves links only — it never hosts or re-streams. Availability isn't guaranteed; adult channels are excluded unless you opt in per list.","No channel lists yet","Add a list, pick one or more countries, and WayHop builds a deduped, auto-refreshing M3U you add to your player.","Filter countries…","selected","Name (optional)","defaults to the country names","Include adult channels — off by default","Check availability every refresh and drop dead channels (the automatic interval checker — slower)","Hold new categories for review before adding them to the box","Auto-refresh","Advanced — block individual channels","Blocklist","Countries","Channels come from the open iptv-org project — one live, auto-updating list per country.","Provider / custom playlist URL","Xtream Codes account","Optional: your provider's Xtream login (host + username + password). WayHop builds the playlist for you; the credentials stay on your router.","+ Add Xtream account","username","password","Remove account","By language or category","Or pick whole iptv-org lists by language or category — the same public, auto-updating source.","Language","Category","Russian","English","Arabic","Persian","Spanish","French","German","Portuguese","Italian","Turkish","Hindi","Chinese","Ukrainian","Polish","Romanian","Greek","Dutch","Czech","Hungarian","Serbian","Croatian","Bulgarian","Hebrew","Thai","Vietnamese","Indonesian","Malay","Japanese","Korean","Azerbaijani","Kazakh","Uzbek","Armenian","Georgian","Tajik","Kyrgyz","Turkmen","Bengali","Urdu","Tamil","News","Sports","Movies","Music","Kids","Entertainment","Documentary","General","Comedy","Culture","Education","Lifestyle","Science","Series","Travel","Weather","Religious","Cooking","Outdoor","Relax","Business","Animation","Classic","Family","Browse public lists","+ Custom list","Public channel lists","Filter…","Added","+ Add","Adding…","Languages","Categories","Free-to-air channels in this country","Channels in this language","Channels in this category","country","language","category","Add open, auto-updating channel lists — by country, language or category — as one deduped M3U your player imports.","Optional: paste your own provider's M3U URL (one per line). Fetched securely; WayHop serves the links, never the stream.","Channels","Preview what's inside and switch off whole categories you don't want (shopping, religious, …). Channels in the categories you keep update automatically.","🔎 Preview & choose channels","Keep all","Cut common junk","Show channels","Reachable","Geo-blocked — needs an in-country exit","Unreachable","loading channels…","This category is cut — check a channel to keep it anyway.","🔍 Check availability","Checking…","No channels.","No channels found for these countries.","Pick a country or add a provider URL first","🔗 custom","Auto-refresh paused","paused","Adult channels included","adult","Health-checked — dead channels dropped","checked","Copy URL","⤓ Export","⎘ Duplicate","↻ Update now","▶ Resume","⏸ Pause","Edit","Delete","Scan in your IPTV player (TiviMate, IPTV Smarters, VLC, Kodi), or copy the URL.","rendering…","Open landing page","QR rendering failed","Copy","⤓ Download","Copy or download this to back up or share the list's setup. Import recreates the list on any WayHop (with a fresh URL).","Paste an exported list JSON here","Paste a list exported from WayHop. It's added as a new list with its own URL.","New channel categories","These categories appeared in your sources since you set up this list. Keep the ones you want; un-check to cut them (excluded from now on).","Cut all","Cut junk","keep","cut","Apply","Edit channel list","Add channel list","Add list","Add at least one country or a provider URL","Saved — your box updates itself; the same link keeps working","List added — it builds shortly; add the link to your player","List deleted","Updating in the background — your box gets the fresh list within a minute","Auto-refresh resumed","That isn't valid JSON","List imported","List duplicated","All kept","Delete list \"{0}\"? Its playlist URL stops working immediately.","Kept {0}, cut {1}","{0} channels","{0} you cut","{0} pruned","{0} adult-filtered","refreshed {0}","first build failed {0} — will retry automatically","first build failed {0} — paused","not refreshed yet — first build runs shortly","Exits: {0}"," — no matching exit; geo-locked channels there may not play"," — all covered","⚠ {0} channels — some TV boxes/players load large lists slowly; cut categories to trim","⚑ {0} new — review","You'll get about {0} of {1} channels — the rest stay off."];
